title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 8
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. In an argument concerning who is a real Ryder the show gets abruptly derailed by mysterious DM group being exposed. Tesions are high and trust and loyalty between the crew is currently in limbo...
